<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV65">
<l>kaṟṟup piṇaimalark kaṇṇiṉ kulamveṉṟō rōkaruma</l>
<l>muṟṟup payiṉṟu ceviyoṭu cāvi yulakamellā</l>
<l>muṟṟum viḻuṅki yumiḻnta pirāṉār tiruvaṭikkī</l>
<l>ḻuṟṟum muṟātu miḷirntakaṇ ṇāyemmai yuṇkiṉṟavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it only [their] being skilfull [and] victorious in the family of blooming</l>
<l>doe eyes? In the sway of Karma, repeatedly glancing sideways , as eyes</l>
<l>that flash, dwelling and not dwelling under the holy feet of the lord who</l>
<l>swallowed [and] spat out all the whole worlds, they eat us up.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
